      "@id": "asbval:assertion/card/task_001/000",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "The Spectra package natively supports import of MS data from mzML, mzXML and netCDF files and through its add-on packages MsBackendMgf, MsBackendMsp and MsBackendMassbank from files in MGF, MSP or MassBank format",
      "asbval:note": "Paper discusses MsBackend implementations (MsBackendMgf, MsBackendMsp, MsBackendMassbank) but does not describe creating a new in-memory test backend or document the virtual class API requirements. The paper focuses on existing backends for file format support, not on implementing a test backend or documenting the MsBackend virtual class interface.",
