      "asbval:evidence_quote": null,
      "asbval:note": "The paper does not discuss memory profiling, benchmarking, or comparison of memory consumption across computational strategies. The paper focuses on annotation workflows, modular infrastructure, and data handling for metabolomics, not on memory optimization or profiling techniques for MS backends.",
