      "asbval:target_artifact_kind": "skill_bundle",
      "asbval:target_claim_field": "research_question",
      "asbval:target_claim_text": "A technique to quantify and compare memory consumption across alternative computational strategies (e.g., whole-load vs. chunk-wise processing) using profiling tools and controlled benchmarks. Applied to mass spectrometry backends, it validates that lazy-loading and factored proc",
