      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms Spectra supports on-disk MS data sources from mzML, mzXML, and netCDF (CDF) formats, but does not discuss parallel or serial chunk-wise processing. The scope description assumes MsBackendMzR exists and is used for this purpose, but MsBackendMzR is not mentioned in the paper.",
