      "asbval:target_claim_field": "scope",
      "asbval:target_claim_text": "When you have a Spectra object backed by an on-disk MS data source (e.g., MsBackendMzR reading mzML, mzXML, or CDF files) and need to process large numbers of spectra in parallel or serial chunks.",
