      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": null,
      "asbval:note": "The paper does not discuss on-the-fly peak data retrieval, dataStorage metadata, or memory profiling considerations for large-scale spectra processing. These are implementation details not covered in the provided passages.",
