      "asbval:target_claim_field": "research_question",
      "asbval:target_claim_text": "Quantify memory consumption and execution latency of R objects before and after data operations using object.size() profiling and timing measurements. This skill is essential when evaluating memory\u2013speed tradeoffs in data structure design, such as choosing between eager pre-popul",
